paragraphs: Hi I am Manas Jain, a 22 year old software engineer baised in Bengaluru, India.
Currently I am impacting as a software developer at Ittiam Systems in Bengaluru, India.
I have completed my bachelor's degree in Computer Science and Engineering from Shri. Govindram Seksaria Institute of Technology and Science, Indore during the term 2016-2020
I am adept to code in Java, Python, Go and C
Team Management and Photography are some of my non-technical skills I am confident about and you will always find me surrounded by friends or clicking pictures.
In my free time you can see me vibing to my music playlist, playing basketball or valorant with my friends, in a Formula 1 or UEFA Champions League streaming party, etc.
